strings.Value: "Do you think it's my first time?"
"I knew you two were dangerous... But now I see how much!"
"We need to do this more often."
{n}After a hot night together, you're helping one another clean up...{/n}
"As usual!" {n}Octavia jokingly slaps Regongar on the nose, and he bites her fingers, laughing.{/n}
"What a wild night... Did you like it?"

{n}Octavia hugs you and Regongar.{/n} "You know what? I love you. Both of you. Do with that whatever you want!"
"What else can you do when you find your love? Spend time together. Drink, laugh, look at the stars. Help {mf|him|her} conquer all the neighboring lands... The everyday joys of lovers!"
